# Scraper & Exam Listing UI Rules

## Scraper Management (Admin Only)
- Protected behind admin middleware
- Source list: table layout with sortable columns
- Status colors: active=green, paused=amber, error=red, pending=gray
- "Scrape Now" triggers BullMQ job, polls for progress
- Real-time log: poll scrape_runs every 3s during active scrape
- Test scrape: inline preview of extracted questions (max 5)

## Add Source Form
- URL field: validate with z.string().url()
- "Test Scrape" calls testScrape mutation → shows preview
- Preview: card with extracted question count + 3 sample questions
- AI Provider selector: reuse <AIProviderSelector mode="single" />
- On save: optimistic update to source list

## Exam Listing (/exams — PUBLIC)
- Server Component for initial load (SEO)
- URL search params synced with filters: /exams?category=pharmacy&status=upcoming
- Category filters: multi-select checkboxes
- Status: single select (All, Upcoming, Active, Past)
- Search: debounced input, searches name + tags + conducting_body
- Cards: uniform height, truncate long descriptions
- Countdown badge: "Exam in 23 days" for upcoming, "Completed" for past
- Pagination: cursor-based (load more button, not page numbers)
- Mobile: filters collapse to bottom sheet, cards stack vertically
- Empty state: friendly illustration + "No exams found"
- SEO: generateMetadata with exam count + category in title

## Home Page Exam Showcase
- Max 6 cards: 3 featured + 3 upcoming
- Auto-rotate featured exams (if > 3)
- "View All Exams →" link to /exams
- Countdown timer on upcoming exam cards
- Responsive: 3 cols desktop, 2 tablet, 1 mobile
